Nutrient data for: STIMOROL GUM SPEARMINT, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210057624
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: sweeteners (sorbitol, isomalt, maltitol, maltitol syrup, aspartame, acesulfame K, sucralose), gum base, bulking agent (E170), flavourings, thickener (E414), humectant (E422), emulsifiers ( E172a, sunflower lecithin), colours ( E171, E141), glazing agent (E903), antioxidant (E321). Contains a source of phenylalanine. Excess consumption may have a laxative effect. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/25/2016
